{
  "stem": "10162.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother used to light the candles Friday night, and I wasn't supposed to touch it until it burns completely down.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I just could not resist, you know, when it was just going to be almost sort of in-- in the delicious, malleable texture or-- or-- or feeling.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just would have to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I know-- knew it was a crime and a sin, but I just had to make something out of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And miraculously, it wound up in my mother's vitrine, what they called.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So as much as she scorned, but it-- at it, she still displayed it with pride.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because when it was thin and it-- and it-- it cooled off, it looked like a-- a fine porcelain.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And also, the Hungarian bread when we were-- we always had bread on the table at meals-- is kind of a glutinous texture also that you can-- you can-- instead of eating it, you can manipulate it under the table and make little heads, and dogs, and animals out of it.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I always did something like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once I was ill and I was doing my thing, maybe with plasticine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then this doctor who used to come to the house said, you do that?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I cannot believe that she made that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how it just sort of worked out that they decided that they should-- they should give me private lessons.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no such thing as sculptor in Debrecen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "However, there were two very well-known painters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I became their student.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I stuck with painting for many years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I actually went back to my original love of sculpture when I came to this country, in stone and wood.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Drastically changing, right?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
